Package hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.util

This package contain utility classes for various Scheduler implementations and two minimalist utility classes that work with Func1 and Action1 classes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionObservable
    The functional observable helper class with the anamorphism, bind and catamorpism basic operators.
    DefaultEdtScheduler
    The default Event Dispatch Thread scheduler implementation.
    DefaultScheduler
    The default implementation of the Scheduler interface used by the Observables methods.
    EdtExecutorService
    The wrapper for the event dispatch thread.
    FunctionIterable
    The functional iterable support with anamorphism, bind and catamorphism.
    SingleLaneExecutor<T>
    A helper class which ensures that each of its queued elements get processed in sequence even on a multi-threaded pool.
